headline: Why Entergy (ETR) is a Great Dividend Stock Right Now
summary: Dividends are one of the best benefits to being a shareholder, but finding a great dividend stock is no easy task. Does Entergy (ETR) have what it takes? Let's find out.

headline: BMO Capital Maintains Outperform on Entergy, Raises Price Target to $112
summary: BMO Capital  analyst James Thalacker   maintains Entergy (NYSE:ETR) with a Outperform and raises the price target from $104 to $112.
